ened and stored in a cool, dry place.","If a smoother chutney is desired, chop <b><strong>5 sec\/speed 5<\/strong><b> at the end of step 4.","Serve the chutney with red meat, game dishes or flavoursome cheese."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","45m","2 jars"]}